### ❓ QUESTIONS API
### ============================================================

@questionId = PASTE_QUESTION_ID_HERE

### [30] Add Question (Admin only) ➕
POST {{baseUrl}}/questions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "type": "mcq",
  "text": "ما هو عدد حروف اللغة العربية؟",
  "options": [
    { "label": "٢٦", "isCorrect": false },
    { "label": "٢٨", "isCorrect": true },
    { "label": "٣٠", "isCorrect": false },
    { "label": "٢٤", "isCorrect": false }
  ],
  "difficulty": "easy"
}

### Expected Response ✅
# Status: 201
# {
#   "message": "Question added successfully",
#   "question": {
#     "_id": "...",
#     "type": "mcq",
#     "text": "ما هو عدد حروف اللغة العربية؟",
#     "options": [...],
#     "difficulty": "easy",
#     "createdAt": "..."
#   }
# }

###

### [31] Add Question - math type ➕
POST {{baseUrl}}/questions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "type": "math",
  "text": "كم يساوي 3 + 5 ؟",
  "answer": "8",
  "difficulty": "easy"
}

### Expected Response ✅
# Status: 201
# { "message": "Question added successfully", "question": { ... } }

###

